Aaron’s Dead Stats

Updated: May 09, 2024 (12:28 MDT)

About

This website is an analysis of my Grateful Dead listening habits using scrobble data collected via last.fm. I have been “scrobbling” or collecting metadata on the music that I have listened to since January 2016. For each song played on one of my devices, a “scrobble” is recorded.

Currently, I have scrobbled 13084 Dead songs, the vast majority of which comes from their extensive catalog of live concert recordings.
